%% Current State: Software Release Process
flowchart LR
    start([Change Request]) --> dev[Develop Update]
    dev --> pr[Open PR / Review]
    pr --> merge[Merge to Main]
    merge --> build[Build Package]
    build --> test[Informal Test]
    test --> decide{Ready to Release?}
    decide -- Yes --> deploy[Deploy Software]
    decide -- No --> rework[Fix and Retry]
    rework --> dev

    classDef gate fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#c0392b,color:#fff
    classDef milestone fill:#2ecc71,stroke:#27ae60,color:#fff
    classDef feedback fill:#f39c12,stroke:#e67e22,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#90caf9,color:#1a237e
    classDef artifact fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#ffcc02,color:#333
    classDef external fill:#e0e0e0,stroke:#9e9e9e,color:#333

    class start external
    class dev,pr,merge,build,test,deploy process
    class decide gate
    class rework feedback
